              "children": {
                "1": {
                  "id": "1",
                  "speaker": "21783519-4c61-4e36-abd4-c9386303cade",
                  "text": "Ah, well. If it was just myself, I surely would. But I'm watching this house on behalf of someone a sight scarier.",
